%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJose%20Palafox%20used%20a%20DST%201031%20exchange%20to%20defer%20taxes%20on%20his%20Portland%20rental%20sale.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strategy%20allows%20reinvestment%20into%20a%20trust%2C%20so%20Palafox%20no%20longer%20has%20to%20manage%20a%20property.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20wasn't%20the%20simplest%20strategy%20to%20execute%20and%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20and%20moving%20parts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20Jose%20Palafox%20took%20advantage%20of%20a%20little-known%20tax%20strategy%20called%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-defer-real-estate-capital-gains-tax-1031-exchange-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDST%201031%20exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20investors%20to%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20a%20rental%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalafox%20was%20ready%20to%20sell%20his%20Portland%20rental%2C%20which%20had%20become%20more%20of%20a%20headache%20than%20a%20cash%20cow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20HOA%20fees%20had%20increased%2C%20my%20taxes%20had%20increased%2C%20and%20rents%20in%20Portland%20had%20gone%20down%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20making%20much%20if%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20San%20Francisco-based%20millennial%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20hadn't%20ever%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20landlord.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20himself%20a%20landlord%20when%20he%20got%20a%20job%20offer%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20while%20living%20in%20Portland.%20Rather%20than%20selling%20his%20primary%20residence%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20converted%20it%20to%20a%20rental%2C%20heeding%20common%20advice%20to%20hold%20onto%20real%20estate%3A%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20told%20me%2C%20'Buy%20a%20house%20and%20don't%20sell%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecuting%20a%20DST%201031%20exchange%2C%20in%20which%20you%20sell%20a%20property%20and%20reinvest%20the%20proceeds%20into%20a%20Delaware%20Statutory%20Trust%20(DST)%2C%20not%20only%20allowed%20him%20to%20defer%20capital%20gains%20tax%20%E2%80%94%20it%20also%20released%20him%20from%20landlord%20responsibilities.%20He%20essentially%20exchanged%20his%20Portland%20condo%20for%20a%20DST%2C%20which%20holds%20commercial%20real%20estate%20assets%2C%20and%20now%20owns%20fractions%20of%20high-grade%20institutional%20properties.%20He%20receives%20a%20%24550%20dividend%20payment%20each%20month%2C%20which%20BI%20verified%20by%20looking%20at%20a%20deposit%20made%20into%20his%20checking%20account%20from%20the%20DST.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalafox%20says%20he's%20bringing%20in%20more%20from%20the%20DST%20than%20he%20was%20when%20he%20was%20renting%20his%20condo%2C%20and%20the%20investment%20is%20completely%20passive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20right%20move%20for%20him%20and%20his%20financial%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20he%20didn't%20need%20to%20touch%20the%20proceeds%20from%20the%20property%20sale%20and%20could%20afford%20to%20reinvest%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20avoided%20a%20tax%20consequence%20while%20gaining%20exposure%20to%20real%20estate%20assets%20he%20could%20never%20have%20afforded%20as%20an%20individual%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20process%2C%20which%20Palafox%20completed%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%20according%20to%20an%20exchange%20statement%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20didn't%20come%20without%20its%20barriers%20to%20entry.%20Here%20are%20the%20challenges%20he%20faced%20before%20and%20during%20the%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20an%20accredited%20investor.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20do%20a%20DST%201031%20exchange%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20what's%20called%20an%20accredited%20investor.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20ways%20to%20qualify%3A%20having%20a%20net%20worth%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20not%20including%20the%20value%20of%20your%20primary%20residence%3B%20having%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%24200%2C000%20as%20an%20individual%20or%20%24300%2C000%20if%20you're%20married%20and%20filing%20jointly%20(this%20is%20how%20Palafox%20qualified)%3B%20or%20having%20certain%20professional%20certifications%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Series%207%2C%20Series%2065%2C%20or%20Series%2082%20licenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you're%20an%20accredited%20investor%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20even%20find%20information%20about%20various%20DST%20sponsors%2C%20noted%20Palfox%2C%20who%20hired%20a%20financial%20advisor%20to%20walk%20him%20through%20his%20options%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20a%20qualified%20investor%20in%20order%20to%20even%20see%20the%20list%20of%20available%20DSTs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Prepare%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20and%20multiple%20parties.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20Palafox's%20experience%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20he%20signed%20about%2010%20documents%20via%20Docusign%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20moving%20parts.%20In%20addition%20to%20his%20advisor%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20to%20list%20and%20sell%20his%20rental%2C%20two%20separate%20title%20companies%20(one%20for%20the%20property%20sale%20and%20another%20for%20the%20DST)%2C%20and%20the%20DST%20sponsor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20had%20to%20find%20a%20qualified%20intermediary%20(QI).%20This%20is%20a%20neutral%20third%20party%20that%20holds%20the%20home%20sale%20proceeds%20until%20the%20investor%20buys%20their%20replacement%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20It%20can%20be%20an%20emotional%20roller%20coaster%2C%20especially%20when%20your%20money%20is%20with%20the%20QI.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20most%20unsettling%20part%20of%20the%20process%20for%20Palafox%20was%20immediately%20after%20he%20sold%20his%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20period%20of%20time%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20my%20money%20was%20from%20the%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20paper%2C%20his%20six-figure%20sale%20proceeds%20were%20in%20an%20escrow%20account%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20beyond%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20I%20docusigned%20and%20the%20general%20say-so%20of%20people%20I'd%20never%20met%20on%20email%20I%20didn't%20really%20know%20how%20I%20would%20get%20my%20money%20back%20if%20I%20had%20to.%20My%20wife%20accused%20me%20of%20getting%20into%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme%20for%20a%20while.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20still%20has%20some%20anxiety%20about%20his%20investment%20because%20it's%20so%20different%20from%20anything%20else%20he%20owns.%20The%20only%20%26quot%3Bproof%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20that%20he%20owns%20anything%20is%20an%20email%20from%20his%20DST%20sponsor%20congratulating%20him%20for%20his%20purchase%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20still%20kind%20of%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20It%20could%20complicate%20your%20tax%20situation.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20am%20not%20looking%20forward%20to%20is%20paying%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Palafox.%20%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20the%20product%20you%20could%20be%20paying%20taxes%20in%20multiple%20additional%20states.%20I%20will%20use%20an%20accountant%20but%20I%20expect%20some%20increased%20costs%20and%20complications%20to%20file%20come%20tax%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20once%20you've%20gotten%20past%20the%20major%20barriers%20to%20entry%20to%20doing%20a%20DST%201031%20exchange%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20still%20a%20lot%20more%20challenging%20and%20in%20some%20ways%20less%20satisfying%20than%20clicking%20a%20button%20on%20your%20favorite%20trading%20app%20and%20buying%20stocks%20or%20crypto%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20ticker%20to%20watch%2C%20these%20are%20boring%20investments%20that%20produce%20boring%20returns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he'd%20deal%20with%20the%20paperwork%20and%20stress%20all%20over%20again%20if%20he%20could%20go%20back%2C%20particularly%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BUPREIT%26quot%3B%20option.%20Palafox%20said%20that%20what%20really%20sold%20him%20on%20this%20strategy%20was%20another%20tax%20code%20%26quot%3Bloophole%2C%26quot%3B%20of%20sorts%2C%20known%20as%20the%20721%20exchange%2C%20or%20UPREIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20a%20DST%20will%20end%20(most%20have%20a%20predetermined%20lifespan%20of%20five%20to%2010%20years)%2C%20at%20which%20point%20his%20options%20are%20%26quot%3Bto%20either%201031%20into%20another%20DST%20or%2C%20ideally%2C%20be%20bought%20by%20a%20REIT%20fund%20that%20wants%20to%20own%20and%20operate%20these%20buildings%20longer%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BUsing%20a%20721%20exchange%2C%20I%20can%20roll%20into%20the%20REIT%20fund%2C%20again%20deferring%20taxes.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20this%20process%2C%20I%20would%20own%20shares%20in%20a%20private%20or%20public%20REIT%2C%20which%20I%20could%20fractionally%20liquidate.%20So%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20sell%20half%20of%20my%20investment%2C%20I%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20DST%2C%20he%20could%20get%20into%20a%20REIT%20without%20causing%20a%20taxable%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20finally%20understood%20the%20flow%20from%20my%20investment%20into%20a%20REIT%20fund%2C%20the%20light%20really%20went%20off%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20saying%2C%20'Wow%2C%20this%20is%20the%20future%2C'%20and%20now%20I'm%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20fan%2C%20I%20guess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdst-1031-exchange-defer-capital-gains-tax-on-home-sale-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732631840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744cb3ffa0140cdd56545da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdst-1031-exchange-defer-capital-gains-tax-on-home-sale-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3