%3BOmead%20has%20essentially%20proven%20he%20can%20stand%20close%20to%20the%20sun%20without%20getting%20burned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfshar%2C%20another%20former%20employee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20like%20the%20final%20boss%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Elon%3A%20Everything%20goes%20through%20him%20first.%26quot%3B%20(This%20employee%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20others%20interviewed%20for%20this%20article%2C%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20Tesla%2C%20Afshar%20studied%20biomedical%20engineering%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Irvine%2C%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20ski%20instructor.%20In%202009%2C%20several%20months%20after%20he%20graduated%2C%20Afshar%2C%20then%2023%2C%20was%20driving%20in%20the%20Westlake%20Village%20neighborhood%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2011%20p.m.%2C%20Afshar%20lost%20control%20of%20the%20car.%20A%20local%20news%20report%20said%20he%20crossed%20into%20the%20median%2C%20knocked%20down%20several%20trees%2C%20and%20finally%20hit%20a%20larger%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmergency%20personnel%20took%20Afshar%20and%20a%20passenger%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2020s%2C%20out%20of%20the%20car%20and%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20critical%20condition%2C%20an%20incident%20report%20said.%20His%20cousin%20Behrad%20Vahidi%20told%20BI%20that%20Afshar%20had%20%26quot%3Bkissed%20death%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfshar%20has%20never%20spoken%20publicly%20about%20the%20crash.%20But%20in%20a%202019%20interview%20with%20his%20younger%20brother%20at%20an%20event%20for%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20Afshar%20defended%20Tesla's%20mission%20of%20making%20driving%20safer%20and%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20unfairly%20maligned%20by%20journalists%20reporting%20on%20crashes%20involving%20the%20company's%20vehicles.%20There%20are%20over%20100%20automobile%20deaths%20per%20day%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20if%20a%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bruns%20into%20someone's%20garage%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20headline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfshar%20seemed%20exasperated%20that%20some%20people%20couldn't%20grasp%20what%20he%20saw%20as%20the%20larger%20picture.%20At%20Tesla%20and%20other%20Musk%20companies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mission%20is%20good%2C%20and%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%20company%20in%202017%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20in%20the%20office%20of%20the%20CEO%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20He%20moved%20to%20Texas%20in%202020%20to%20oversee%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Gigafactory%2C%20which%20he%20took%20from%20groundbreaking%20to%20grand%20opening%20in%20less%20than%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-07-21%2Ftesla-tsla-executive-under-scrutiny-in-internal-probe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20he%20was%20part%20of%20a%20project%20involving%20plans%20for%20a%20large%20glass%20structure.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos%2Fa-glass-house-for-elon-musk-sparks-internal-tesla-probe-9a121db5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20project%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BProject%2042%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20internally%20believed%20to%20involve%20building%20a%20glass%20house%20for%20Musk.%20Tesla%20launched%20an%20internal%20investigation%20into%20Project%2042%20in%202022%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20The%20Department%20of%20Justice%20and%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-doj-sec-investigation-project-42-glass-house-elon-musk-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20separate%20inquiries%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Project%2042%2C%20the%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos%2Ftesla-elon-musk-glass-house-doj-sec-investigation-c723166b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20of%20those%20investigations%20is%20unclear.%20The%20SEC%20declined%20to%20confirm%20the%20existence%20of%20such%20an%20investigation.%20The%20DOJ%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Musk%20has%20previously%20said%20he%20does%20not%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20glass%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20current%20and%20former%20colleagues%20said%20Afshar%20became%20lower%20profile%20at%20Tesla%20in%202022%20but%20continued%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20Musk.%20Afshar%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-11-10%2Ftesla-official-afshar-turns-up-at-spacex-in-new-starship-role%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20SpaceX%20in%20late%202022.%20The%20Financial%20Times%20reported%20that%20Afshar%20also%20assisted%20with%20Musk's%20acquisition%20of%20Twitter%2C%20now%20X%2C%20and%20with%20cost-cutting%20initiatives%20at%20the%20social-media%20company%20in%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225791%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Teslas%20cars%20on%20the%20production%20line%20of%20the%20company's%20Austin%2C%20Texas%20Gigafactory.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669a9bd180d4d5da13d573b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20Teslas%20cars%20on%20the%20production%20line%20of%20the%20company's%20Austin%2C%20Texas%20Gigafactory.%20Afshar%20oversaw%20construction%20of%20the%20facility.%3Cp%3EGetty%2F%20Suzanne%20Cordeiro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERecords%20of%20text%20messages%20from%20Afshar%20to%20Musk%2C%20included%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20related%20to%20Musk's%20purchase%20of%20Twitter%2C%20underscore%20their%20close%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20love%20you%20and%20are%20always%20behind%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Afshar%20wrote%20in%20April%202022%2C%20the%20day%20after%20Musk%20made%20an%20unsolicited%20offer%20to%20buy%20the%20social-media%20company.%20%26quot%3BNot%20having%20a%20global%20platform%20that%20is%20truly%20free%20speech%20is%20dangerous%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Musk%20responded%2C%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20it%20in%20those%20court%20documents.%20Other%20court%20documents%20show%20that%20Afshar%20later%20invested%20in%20Twitter%20through%20a%20limited%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfshar%20had%20formally%20returned%20to%20Tesla%20by%20early%202024%2C%20five%20former%20employees%20said%2C%20though%20two%20of%20those%20people%20said%20Afshar%20was%20regularly%20operating%20in%20the%20background%20even%20before%20his%20official%20homecoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20photos%20of%20Afshar%2C%20he%20is%20nearly%20always%20at%20Musk's%20side%3A%20onstage%20at%20Tesla's%20Cyber%20Rodeo%20party%3B%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20Tesla's%20manufacturing%20executives%20in%20Shanghai%3B%20and%20at%20a%20dinner%20for%20brainstorming%20robotaxi%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfiwUE_2JhvY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Cyber%20Rodeo%20at%20Giga%20Texas%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOmead%20is%20similar%20to%20Elon%3A%20You%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20talk%20about%20anything%20or%20everything%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Afshar's%20former%20skip-level%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Zhu%20and%20Musk's%20family%20office%20manager%20Jared%20Birchall%2C%20Afshar%20has%20left%20barely%20a%20trace%20in%20the%20public%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20given%20only%20two%20known%20on-the-record%20interviews%20to%20journalists%3A%20one%20to%20Walter%20Isaacson%2C%20for%20his%202023%20biography%20of%20Musk%2C%20and%20another%20to%20Time%20magazine%20when%20the%20publication%20named%20Musk%20%26quot%3BPerson%20of%20the%20Year%26quot%3B%20in%202021.%20Election%20and%20campaign-finance%20records%20indicate%20Afshar%20has%20made%20no%20political%20contributions%20and%20has%20voted%20only%20once%2C%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20work%2C%20Afshar%20appears%20to%20lead%20a%20modest%20existence%20in%20line%20with%20his%20corporate%20reputation%20for%20cost-cutting%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20moved%20to%20Austin%20in%202020%2C%20he%20rented%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment.%20That%20year%20he%20received%20%2410%20million%20worth%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-salary-database-elon-musk-pay-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20shares%20as%20a%20bonus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%202021%20he%20paid%20%241.6%20million%20for%20a%20newly%20constructed%20three-bedroom%20home%20in%20what%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20described%20in%20a%20listing%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Beclectic%26quot%3B%20neighborhood.%20For%20at%20least%20a%20year%20after%20Afshar%20moved%20in%2C%20the%20home%20across%20the%20street%20had%20broken%20windows%20and%20stripped%20siding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20colleagues%20said%20they%20observed%20occasional%20micromanaging%20tendencies%20in%20his%20Texas%20Gigafactory%20role%2C%20but%20they%20also%20emphasized%20his%20warmth%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cofounder-martin-eberhard-on-company-culture-elon-musk-firings-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20high-octane%20corporate%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20workers%20praised%20Afshar%20for%20working%20to%20improve%20the%20employee%20experience%2C%20including%20buying%20Texas-style%20belt%20buckles%20to%20celebrate%20the%20factory's%20launch%20and%20planning%20a%20factorywide%20party%20after%20the%20site%20received%20a%20certificate%20of%20occupancy%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20interview%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20Afshar%20described%20his%20devotion%20to%20the%20automaker%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20missed%20birthdays%20and%20felt%20anxious%20about%20being%20away%20from%20his%20phone%20for%20even%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20high-pressure%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20definitely%20one%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Tesla%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A2488946012%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E248-894-6012%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomead-afshar-executive-tesla-profile-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732630527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6734eec6ede4eeae39273c19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomead-afshar-executive-tesla-profile-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Known%20for%20his%20perfectionism%20and%20total%20dedication%20to%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Omead%20Afshar%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20Tesla's%20most%20powerful%20executives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Kay%2CKatherine%