mes%20ending%20life%20at%20birth%20or%20soon%20thereafter%20while%2C%20at%20other%20times%2C%20waiting%20a%20century%20or%20so%20before%20paying%20a%20visit.%20To%20date%2C%20I've%20been%20very%20lucky%2C%20but%2C%20before%20long%2C%20he%20will%20get%20around%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Buffett%20said%2C%20reflecting%20on%20how%20he%20thought%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20Susie%2C%20would%20outlive%20him%20and%20subsequently%20donate%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20their%20fortune%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthat%20was%20not%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20letter%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.berkshirehathaway.com%2Fnews%2Fnov2524.pdf%5C%22%3EBERKSHIRE%20HATHAWAY%20INC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20%241.2%20billion%20donations%2C%20his%20class%20A%20shares%20in%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20-%20which%20accounts%20for%2099.5%25%20of%20his%20%24150%20billion%20wealth%20-%20have%20reduced%20to%20206%2C363%20shares%20after%20he%20gave%20way%20almost%2056.6%25%20of%20his%20shareholdings%20since%20his%20pledge%20in%202006.%20He%20is%20currently%20the%20sixth%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202004%2C%20before%20Susie%2C%20my%20first%20wife%2C%20died%2C%20the%20two%20of%20us%20owned%20508%2C998%20Class%20A%20shares.%20For%20decades%2C%20we%20had%20both%20thought%20that%20she%20would%20outlive%20me%20and%20subsequently%20distribute%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20our%20large%20fortune.%20That%20was%20not%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20New%20Will%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berkshire%20CEO%20made%20changes%20to%20his%20will%2C%20detailing%20how%20he%20plans%20to%20donate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20wealth%20after%20his%20death.%20Mr%20Buffett%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20first%20wife%20Susie%20had%20%26quot%3Blong%20encouraged%26quot%3B%20their%20children%20in%20small%20philanthropic%20activities%20and%20had%20been%20pleased%20with%20their%20enthusiasm%2C%20diligence%20and%20results.%20Since%202006%2C%20their%20philanthropic%20activities%20have%20dramatically%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20his%20three%20children%20-%20Susie%2C%20Howie%20and%20Peter%20-%20will%20gradually%20distribute%20all%20of%20his%20Berkshire%20holdings%20that%20account%20for%2099.5%25%20of%20his%20wealth.%20In%20his%20lifetime%2C%20Mr%20Buffett%20has%20donated%20more%20than%20%2460%20billion%20of%20his%20wealth%20to%20various%20foundations%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20which%2C%20approximately%20%2443%20billion%2C%20to%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%20run%20by%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20reflected%20upon%20mortality%2C%20relationships%20and%20the%20fickle%20nature%20of%20life%2C%20he%20talked%20about%20a%20downside%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bgood%20fortune%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20expected%20life%20span%20of%20my%20children%20has%20materially%20diminished%20since%20the%202006%20pledge.%20They%20are%20now%2071%2C%2069%20and%2066.%20I've%20never%20wished%20to%20create%20a%20dynasty%20or%20pursue%20any%20plan%20that%20extended%20beyond%20the%20children.%20I%20know%20the%20three%20well%20and%20trust%20them%20completely.%20Future%20generations%20are%20another%20matter.%20Who%20can%20foresee%20the%20priorities%2C%20intelligence%20and%20fidelity%20of%20successive%20generations%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20distribution%20of%20extraordinary%20wealth%20amid%20what%20may%20be%20a%20far%20different%20philanthropic%20landscape%3F%20Still%2C%20the%20massive%20wealth%20I've%20collected%20may%20take%20longer%20to%20deploy%20than%20my%20children%20live.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Buffett%20has%20assigned%20three%20potential%20successor%20trustees%20for%20the%20distribution%20of%20wealth%2C%20each%20being%20well-known%20to%20his%20children%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20younger%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20hopes%20that%20the%20trustees%20stay%20on%20the%20waitlist%2C%20and%20his%20children%20fulfil%20the%20responsibility%20in%20their%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20children%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bunanimously%26quot%3B%20decide%20on%20how%20to%20donate%20his%20wealth%2C%20a%20caveat%20in%20his%20will%2C%20which%20he%20explained%20in%20his%20letter%20through%20the%20unpleasant%20reality%20of%20philanthropy%20and%20those%20who%20can%20distribute%20huge%20sums%20are%20forever%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Btargets%20of%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'One%20Suggestion%20For%20All%20Parents'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20one%20further%20suggestion%20for%20all%20parents%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20of%20modest%20or%20staggering%20wealth.%20When%20your%20children%20are%20mature%2C%20have%20them%20read%20your%20will%20before%20you%20sign%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20sure%20each%20child%20understands%20both%20the%20logic%20for%20your%20decisions%20and%20the%20responsibilities%20they%20will%20encounter%20upon%20your%20death.%20If%20any%20have%20questions%20or%20suggestions%2C%20listen%20carefully%20and%20adopt%20those%20found%20sensible.%20You%20don't%20want%20your%20children%20asking%20%26quot%3BWhy%3F%26quot%3B%20in%20respect%20to%20testamentary%20decisions%20when%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732629300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2F8t9tcl7o_warren-buffett-reuters_625x300_26_February_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwarren-buffet-donates-1-2-billion-shares-detailed-plan-on-donating-wealth-7111118%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett%2C%20philanthropist%20and%20multi-billionaire%20CEO%20of%20American%20multinational%20conglomerate%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20has%20donated%20another%20%241.2%20bil