us%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20failing%20to%20curb%20a%20spike%20in%20violence%20against%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20India%20also%20condemned%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20Hindu%20priest.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20urged%20the%20Bangladeshi%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Hindus%20and%20all%20other%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20noted%20with%20deep%20concern%20the%20arrest%20and%20denial%20of%20bail%20to%20Shri%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Sammilit%20Sanatan%20Jagran%20Jote.%20This%20incident%20follows%20the%20multiple%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%20by%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20noted%20that%20there%20are%20several%20documented%20cases%20of%20arson%20and%20looting%20of%20minorities'%20homes%20and%20business%20establishments%2C%20as%20well%20as%20theft%2C%20vandalism%20and%20desecration%20of%20deities%20and%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20while%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20these%20incidents%20remain%20at%20large%2C%20charges%20should%20be%20pressed%20against%20a%20religious%20leader%20presenting%20legitimate%20demands%20through%20peaceful%20gatherings%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732626360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fifdhdp4g_bangladesh-violence_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsupporters-of-arrested-hindu-priest-thrashed-outside-bangladesh-court-7110578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Clashes%20erupted%20between%20police%20and%20supporters%20of%20arrested%20Hindu%20priest%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20outside%20a%20court%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Chattogran%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsupporters-of-arrested-hindu-priest-thrashed-outside-bangladesh-court-7110578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trudeau%20reacted%20to%20Trump's%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20products%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732626203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115699985%2Cimgsize-56664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhow-trudeau-reacted-to-trumps-25-tariffs-on-canadian-products%2Farticleshow%2F115699667.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Trump's%20rationale%20ties%20these%20tariffs%20to%20immigration%20and%20drug%20issues%2C%20economists%20and%20trade%20experts%20often%20caution%20that%20such%20measures%20can%20disrupt%20supply%20chains%2C%20increase%20costs%20for%20American%20businesses%20and%20consumers%2C%20and%20provoke%20retaliatory%20actions%20from%20trading%20partners%2C%20potentially%20escalating%20into%20broader%20trade%20conflicts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alert%20SBI%20Staff%20Save%20Senior%20Citizen%20From%2013-Lakh%20'Digital%20Arrest'%20Scam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20and%20its%20staff%20are%20often%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20criticism%20and%20the%20subject%20of%20memes%20such%20as%20'%3Cem%3Elunch%20ke%20baad%20aana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(come%20after%20lunch)'%2C%20but%20SBI%20says%20they%20have%20stopped%20three%20cases%20of%20digital%20frauds%2C%20thanks%20to%20alert%20employees%20who%20benefitted%20from%20training%20about%20cyber%20frauds%20given%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20AC%20guards%20branch%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20a%20bank%20officer%20Surya%20Swathi%20managed%20to%20save%20a%20senior%20citizen%20from%20being%20conned%20of%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20through%20'digital%20arrest'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScamsters%20had%20targeted%20a%2061-year-old%20child%20specialist%2C%20who%20was%20a%20long-term%20customer%20of%20the%20bank.%20The%20senior%20citizen%20was%20told%20that%20he%20was%20under%20digital%20arrest%20and%20must%20not%20tell%20anyone%20about%20it.%20The%20customer%20reached%20the%20bank%20and%20told%20an%20associate%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20break%20Fixed%20Deposits%20and%20withdraw%20the%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20associate%2C%20Surya%20Swathi%20D%2C%20noticed%20that%20the%20customer%20was%20tense%20and%20asked%20him%20what%20was%20the%20matter.%20The%20customer%20said%20he%20needed%20to%20withdraw%20the%20amount%20for%20personal%20reasons.%20Not%20convinced%2C%20the%20bank%20associate%20took%20him%20to%20the%20manager.%20Kumar%20Goud%2C%20the%20branch%20manager%2C%20said%20that%20the%20customer%20told%20them%20that%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20buy%20property.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20asked%20where%20he%20was%20buying%20the%20property%2C%20the%20customer%20said%20he%20had%20not%20seen%20it%20yet.%20This%20made%20us%20more%20suspicious%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Swathi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20staff%20said%20they%20asked%20the%20customer%20to%20return%20with%20a%20family%20member.%20%26quot%3BWe%20denied%20to%20transfer%20the%20money%20for%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20manager%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20occasion%2C%20the%20customer%20entered%20the%20branch%20and%20did%20not%20go%20to%20Ms%20Swathi's%20kiosk%2C%20since%20she%20had%20not%20allowed%20the%20transaction%20the%20previous%20day%20and%20fearing%20that%20she%20would%20ask%20him%20questions.%20He%20headed%20to%20another%20associate%2C%20but%20by%20then%2C%20the%20branch%20staff%20had%20been%20alerted%20about%20the%20elderly%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20third%20visit%2C%20Swathi%20showed%20the%20customer%20an%20article%20on%20the%20PM's%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%20where%20he%20said%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20digital%20arrest.%20She%20then%20connected%20him%20to%201930%2C%20the%20national%20helpline%20for%20reporting%20cybercrime%2C%20where%20he%20was%20told%20that%20there%20were%20others%20like%20him%20who%20had%20got%20cheated%20in%20the%20name%20of%20as%20'digital%20arrest'.%20After%20three%20days%20of%20torture%2C%20the%20elderly%20customer%20was%20convinced%20that%20he%20was%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20spammed%20and%20he%20hung%20up%20on%20the%20scamster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20customer%20has%20said%20that%20during%20his%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20branch%2C%20he%20was%20on%20a%20call%20with%20the%20scamster%20who%20kept%20telling%20him%20not%20to%20trust%20the%20bank%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20'Digital%20Arrest'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Digital%20arrest'%20is%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20fraud%20in%20which%20fraudsters%20tell%20the%20target%20that%20he%20or%20she%20is%20under%20'digital'%20or%20'virtual'%20arrest%20and%20must%20remain%20connected%20to%20them%20over%20a%20video%20or%20audio%20call.%20The%20target%20is%20told%20that%20he%2Fshe%20cannot%20tell%20anyone%20else%20that%20they%20are%20under%20a%20'digital%20arrest'%20and%20the%20surveillance%20does%20not%20end%20till%20the%20money%20is%20transferred%20to%20the%20fraudsters'%20accounts.%20Police%20have%20stressed%20in%20several%20advisories%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20called%20'digital%20arrest'%20or%20'virtual%20arrest'%2C%20but%20the%20rise%20in%20such%20incidents%20shows%20that%20the%20message%20has%20not%20reached%20a%20large%20section.%20The%20preferred%20targets%20of%20such%20fraud%20are%20senior%20citizens%20who%20are%20not%20very%20savvy%20with%20technology%20and%20are%20easily%20duped%20by%20fraudsters%20into%20following%20their%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732626060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fk927c0d