Cli%3ECanadian%20energy%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20were%20worth%20%24128%20billion%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20took%20aim%20at%20three%20of%20America's%20biggest%20trading%20partners%20on%20Monday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mexico-canada-china-tariffs-january-20-trade-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncing%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20imports%20from%20China%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20received%2083%25%20of%20Mexico's%20exports%20and%2075%25%20of%20Canada's%20exports%20last%20year%2C%20official%20data%20shows.%20Mexico%20worth%20%24379%20billion%20worth%20of%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20Canadian%20exports%20topping%20%24309%20billion%2C%20the%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20reacted%20to%20Trump's%20latest%20tariff%20threats%20by%20betting%20on%20the%20greenback%20and%20paring%20their%20exposure%20to%20vulnerable%20assets.%20The%20US%20dollar%20strengthened%20against%20the%20Canadian%20dollar%20and%20the%20Mexican%20peso%2C%20while%20stock%20markets%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20dipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20should%20prepare%20for%20immediate%20volatility%20in%20sectors%20such%20as%20automotive%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20agriculture%20%E2%80%94%20industries%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20trade%20agreements%20and%20foreign%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Nigel%20Green%2C%20CEO%20of%20deVere%20Group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20some%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20industries%20that%20could%20be%20affected%20by%20Trump's%20new%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285a96b11-42b7-413f-88dc-6c635f8dce66%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECanada%20is%20the%20top%20supplier%20of%20crude%20oil%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sold%20mineral%20fuels%2C%20oils%2C%20and%20distillation%20products%20worth