hards%20and%20a%20third%20unidentified%20person%20worked%20together%20at%20Lululemon%20stores%20in%20Roseville%20and%20Woodbury%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20to%20walk%20away%20with%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20merchandise%2C%20according%20to%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20as%20per%20news%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20say%20more%20than%20%2450%2C000%20in%20Lululemon%20goods%20were%20found%20in%20suitcases%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20suspects'%20hotel%20room%20in%20Bloomington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20total%20loss%20to%20Lululemon%20with%20Richards%2C%20Lawes-Richards%20and%20their%20group%20(the%20company)%20identified%20so%20far%20is%20closer%20to%20%241%2C000%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20court%20documents%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20outstanding%20work%20of%20the%20Roseville%20Police%20investigators%20-%20including%20their%20new%20Retail%20Crime%20Unit%20-%20as%20well%20as%20other%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20these%20individuals%20accused%20of%20this%20massive%20retail%20theft%20operation%20have%20been%20caught%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20attorney's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20November%2018.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20to%20hold%20these%20defendants%20accountable%20and%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20our%20law%20enforcement%20partners%20and%20retail%20merchants%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20retail%20theft%20in%20our%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732622220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fol4ofdc8_sholifting_625x300_26_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-couple-masterminds-1-million-shoplifting-scheme-targeting-lululemon-stores-across-states-7110432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Connecticut%20couple%20is%20accused%20of%20running%20a%20large-scale%20theft%20ring%20targeting%20Lululemon%20stores%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20causing%20losses%20of%20ne