0franchise%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20her%20career%2C%20but%20it%20was%20also%20the%20reason%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bwas%20taken%20down%20publicly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20played%20Elizabeth%20Swann%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20nobleman-turned-pirate%2C%20in%20four%20of%20the%20five%20movies%2C%20alongside%20Orlando%20Bloom%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohnny-depp-amber-heard-relationship-timeline-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohnny%20Depp%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20a%20main%20character%20for%20the%20first%20three%20adventures%2C%20but%20did%20not%20return%20for%202011's%20%26quot%3BOn%20Stranger%20Tides.%26quot%3B%20Knightly%20reprised%20the%20role%20for%20a%20brief%20cameo%20at%20the%20end%20of%202017's%20%26quot%3BDead%20Men%20Tell%20No%20Tales.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FTheNumbers.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETheNumbers.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20franchise%20made%20Disney%20%244.5%20billion%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20but%20critics%20said%20her%20performance%20was%20wooden.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fcelebrity%2Farticle%2Fkeira-knightley-turning-40-black-doves-0pt7gcdjh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20London%20published%20on%20Sunday%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20funny%20thing%20when%20you%20have%20something%20that%20was%20making%20and%20breaking%20you%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20seen%20as%20shit%20because%20of%20them%2C%20and%20yet%20because%20they%20did%20so%20well%20I%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20do%20the%20films%20that%20I%20ended%20up%20getting%20Oscar%20nominations%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20the%20most%20successful%20films%20I'll%20ever%20be%20a%20part%20of%2C%20and%20they%20were%20the%20reason%20that%20I%20was%20taken%20down%20publicly.%20So%20they're%20a%20very%20confused%20place%20in%20my%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnightley%20said%20she%20wouldn't%20appear%20in%20another%20major%20franchise%20following%20her%20experience%20with%20%26quot%3BPirates%20of%20the%20Caribbean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20hours%20are%20insane.%20It's%20years%20of%20your%20life%2C%20you%20have%20no%20control%20over%20where%20you're%20filming%2C%20how%20long%20you're%20filming%2C%20what%20you're%20filming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnightley%20previously%20spoke%20about%20the%20negative%20side%20of%20fame%20in%202018%2C%20when%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-news%2Fawards-chatter-podcast-keira-knightley-colette-1147393%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20took%20a%20year%20off%20from%20acting%20at%20age%2022%20because%20%26quot%3BI%20literally%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20worthless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpirates-of-the-caribbean-original-movie-cast-then-now-photos-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloom%2C%20who%20played%20%3C%2Fa%3ESwann's%20love%20interest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpirates-of-the-caribbean-original-movie-cast-then-now-photos-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWill%20Turner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20also%20shared%20his%20reservations%20about%20starring%20in%20the%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2014%2Ffilm%2Fawards%2Forlando-bloom-on-his-career-as-he-gets-a-star-on-the-hollywood-walk-of-fame-1201150520%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVariety%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20after%20he%20finished%20%26quot%3BPirates%20of%20the%20Caribbean%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20realized%20he%20hadn't%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20experiment%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20because%20he%20had