nsive%20deportation%20plan%20prioritizing%20the%20removal%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20he%20says%20should%20have%20been%20deported%20under%20previous%20administrations.%20Homan's%20plan%20contrasts%20sharply%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20approach%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20record%20illegal%20border%20crossings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fyou-better-start-packing-now-trumps-border-czar-tom-homan-unveils-tough-deportation-plan%2Farticleshow%2F115678626.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fyou-better-start-packing-now-trumps-border-czar-tom-homan-unveils-tough-deportation-plan%2Famp_articleshow%2F115678626.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fyou-better-start-packing-now-trumps-border-czar-tom-homan-unveils-tough-deportation-plan%2Famp_articleshow%2F115678626.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Love%20for%20Ragas%20as%20a%20Baby%20Led%20This%20Musical%20Prodigy%20to%20a%20Grammy%20Nomination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20Grammy-nominated%20singer%2C%20flautist%2C%20and%20composer%2C%20remembers%20an%20incredible%20story%20her%20parents%20once%20told%20her.%20She%20was%20just%2018%20months%20old%20when%20her%20parents%20took%20her%20to%20a%20Carnatic%20music%20concert%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Like%20most%20toddlers%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20patience%20to%20sit%20through%20it%20and%20instead%20played%20with%20other%20toddlers%20in%20a%20nearby%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Varijashree%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20concert%2C%20my%20father%2C%20H%20S%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20apparently%20heard%20me%20scream%20something.%20Mind%20you%2C%20I%20could%20not%20even%20form%20a%20sentence%20at%20that%20time.%20But%20he%20later%20figured%20out%20that%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20say%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20song%20being%20performed%20at%20that%20very%20moment%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20from%20the%20concert%2C%20her%20father%20was%20determined%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20what%20had%20just%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20at%20home%2C%20my%20father%20sang%20a%20variety%20of%20classical%20compositions%20from%20different%20composers%2C%20and%20as%20he%20tells%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20form%20and%20structure%20of%20about%2040%20ragas%20(musical%20modes%20in%20Carnatic%20music)%20with%20whatever%20limited%20syllables%20I%20could%20pronounce%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20observed%20early%20on%20that%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98gift%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20incident%20occurred%20when%20Varijashree%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20By%20this%20age%2C%20she%20was%20already%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192140%2Fmysore-maharaja-wadiyar-western-classical-music-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%20vocal%20performances%20to%20small%20audiences.%20And%20this%20particular%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20one%20of%20her%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20concept%20of%20the%20concert%20was%20that%20I%20would%20sing%20for%20an%20hour.%20Many%20musicians%20attended%20this%20concert%2C%20and%20after%20my%20hour-long%20performance%2C%20they%20sang%20a%20set%20of%20compositions%20in%20100%20different%20%3Cem%3Eragas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20identify%20each%20%3Cem%3Eraga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20did%20successfully.%20This%20concert%20was%20filmed%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20person%20who%20recorded%20it%20lost%20the%20VHS%20tape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIaLqkeKx814%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20beginnings%20as%20a%20child%20prodigy%20in%20Carnatic%20music%20to%20recording%20%E2%80%98A%20Rock%20Somewhere%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20inimitable%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar%20%E2%80%94%20nominated%20this%20year%20for%20a%20Grammy%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Global%20Music%20Performance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Varijashree%20has%20undertaken%20a%20remarkable%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20musician%20with%20a%20classical%20foundation%20who%20has%20since%20expanded%20into%20diverse%20cross-cultural%20and%20interdisciplinary%20styles%2C%20this%20Grammy%20nomination%20feels%20like%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20not%20just%20this%20song%20but%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316118%2Fbengaluru-interactive-indian-music-experience-museum-bollywood-songs-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusical%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20have%20undertaken%20so%20far.%20It%20is%20a%20milestone%20that%20reassures%20me%20that%20the%20direction%20I%20am%20taking%20%5Bcreatively%5D%20is%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20nomination%20fuels%20any%20independent%20artist%20out%20there%20to%20have%20a%20great%20and%20enriching%20creative%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMusic%20permeating%20through%20the%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20and%20my%20mother%2C%20T%20V%20Rama%2C%20an%20accomplished%20vocalist%2C%20were%20my%20first%20gurus.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20everything%20started%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memories%20as%20a%20toddler%20are%20few%2C%20but%20they%20come%20back%20to%20her%20in%20flashes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20vividly%20remember%20sitting%20through%20%3Cem%3EAppa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(father)%20flute%20lessons%20that%20he%20would%20give%20to%20students%20at%20home%20(he%20still%20avidly%20teaches%20to%20this%20day).%20Just%20being%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20I%20remember%20how%20the%20sound%20of%20my%20father%20playing%20the%20flute%20used%20to%20permeate%20the%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22