v%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAjPpWAp78d%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Festival%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20(%40festivaljazzalparque)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20album%20is%20a%20genre-defying%20fusion%20of%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20folk%2C%20and%20global%20rhythms%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20widely%20praised%20for%20its%20unique%20sound.%20It%20celebrates%20Indian%20%3Cem%3Eragas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20various%20formats%20and%20incorporates%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20folk%20and%20classical%20percussion%20and%20melodic%20instruments%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%2040%20musicians%20contributed%20to%20this%20record%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F81965%2Fforeigners-indian-classical-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Indian%20sounds%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20context%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20two-week%20production%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20another%20month%20in%20Spain.%20Besides%20Michael%2C%20we%20also%20had%20another%20co-producer%20on%20board%20%E2%80%94%20my%20friend%20and%20accomplished%20percussionist%20Pramat%20Kiran%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8uBJzibp-XI%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D