20has%20set%20up%20Project%20Kishori%20in%20over%20100%20schools%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20Prazna%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20in%20creating%20menstrual%20health%20awareness%20among%20schoolchildren%2C%20especially%20in%20marginalised%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CSanitary%20pads%20are%20affordable%20now%2C%20the%20Government%20also%20hands%20them%20out.%20But%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20women%20who%20come%20from%20the%20labour%20class%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20underwear%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preeti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20women%20prioritise%20hygiene%20during%20menstruation%2C%20the%20foundation%20gives%20women%20a%20comprehensive%20kit%20of%20essentials%20that%20includes%20underwear%2C%20garbage%20bags%20(to%20teach%20proper%20disposal)%2C%20antiseptic%20liquids%20for%20hygienic%20wash%2C%20and%20paper%20soaps%20to%20encourage%20proper%20handwashing%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20kits%2C%20Project%20Kishori%20largely%20focuses%20on%20educating%20girls%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20helping%20them%20understand%20the%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20them%20to%20ask%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20over%20100%20schools%20within%20two%20months%2C%20both%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur.%20And%20these%20are%20remote%20areas%20where%20nobody%20ever%20goes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20mentions.%20Through%20this%20outreach%2C%20Prazna%20has%20already%20educated%20over%2020%2C000%20women%20on%20menstruation%20and%20hygiene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20its%20approach%20to%20breaking%20down%20the%20taboos%20around%20menstruation%20through%20peer-to-peer%20interaction.%20In%20each%20school%