79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDeepak%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Chaiwalas%E2%80%99%20because%20of%20their%20long-winded%20history%20with%20tea.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20tea%20that%20is%20superimposed%20against%20a%20rich%20history%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20land%20on%20which%20the%20homestay%20now%20stands.%20As%20Deepak%20shares%2C%20it%20dates%20back%20to%201857%2C%20when%20it%20was%20first%20established%20by%20the%20British!%20The%20estate%20saw%20decades%20of%20continuous%20cultivation%20and%20even%20survived%20an%20earthquake%20which%20struck%20the%20region%20in%201905.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Lodge%20at%20Wah%3A%20Inspired%20by%20local%20traditions%20and%20ideas%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Surya%20Prakash%2C%20a%20fourth-generation%20tea%20virtuoso%2C%20recalls%20the%20vacations%20he%20spent%20at%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tea%20estate%20as%20some%20of%20his%20best.%20However%2C%20these%20visits%20were%20short-lived%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20family%20home%20in%20Kangra.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20such%20trip%20that%20Deepak%20had%20his%20moment%20of%20catharsis.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home.%20A%20sustainable%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reasons%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20on%20tea%20estates%2C%20and%20have%20always%20enjoyed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373216%2Faashraya-on-the-ganga-rishikesh-depi-chaudhry-sustainable-eco-friendly-homestays-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20